OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FLow cloud
OL,6,Fwith some drizzle likely lingering on
OL,7,Fwestern hills overnight. Elsewhere,
OL,8,Fdrier with variable cloud and some
OL,9,Fclear spells, especially to the east
OL,10,Fof higher ground. Mild.
OL,11,
OL,12,CThursday:FCloudy with spells of rain,
OL,13,Flocally heavy, moving erratically
OL,14,Fnortheastwards across all parts during
OL,15,FThursday. Rain easing into the
OL,16,Fafternoon. Rather warm and muggy.
OL,17,FLight winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
