OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:
OL,6,FChangeable and often cloudy through
OL,7,Fthis period, with some spells of rain
OL,8,For showers moving erratically
OL,9,Feastwards. Perhaps drier with warm
OL,10,Fsunny spells into the weekend, with
OL,11,Ftemperatures climbing.
